me modes!</strong> Choose between three different game modes: high score, speedrun and endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose your own difficulty! \u00a0</strong>If standard difficulty isn't for you, you can choose from randomised recipe book pages. Or try blackout mode with reduced brightness.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Heavy Duty Tape Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286170/header.jpg?t=1732012911","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 18.04<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.4 GHz or faster processor<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 512 MB display memory<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1200 MB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Mac OS X 10.5<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.33 GHz or faster processor<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 512 MB display memory<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257066478,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066478/movie480.mp4?t=1729864541","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066478/movie_max.mp4?t=1729864541"},"name":"Krax Ca-caw Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257066478/16073b1ac47ffea041a407dfc6ac43a73a9d033f/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1729864541","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066478/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1729864541","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066478/movie_m